text: Fomichevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bulgakovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 234 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 36 km from Ufa, 6 km from Bulgakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Fomichevo, Republic of Bashkortostan
